{"word":"G2134 - εὐνουχίζω - eunouchízō - yoo-noo-khid'-zo - Make…eunuch","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">εὐνουχίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">eunouchízō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">yoo-noo-khid'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Make…eunuch</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அண்ணகர்களாயிரு"},{"paragraph":"to castrate, to unman"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2135 - εὐνοῦχος - eunoûchos - yoo-noo'-khos/2135\">G2135</a>; to <i>castrate</i> (figuratively <i>live unmarried</i>): - make . . . eunuch.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}